{"tid":414042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"塵世間有咩慘得過比自己最愛嘅人冷淡","createTime":"2017-09-26T01:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T02:56:41.000Z","uid":124942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60995dd4fd35fbd0af096a17b13a622912ea51e4","tid":414042,"uid":124942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:54:37.000Z","msg":"如題，明明大家結完婚一直都相親相愛，因為一次工作上失去咗自信嘅發脾氣，令到個老婆親口講喺屋企有壓力，而到e一刻對自己都仲係冷冷淡淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利：已經講晒對唔住、原諒我、比次機會<br />\n<br />\n女人，我真係摸唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cdbd43c30a3ae712e34b279656eed75906c61e","tid":414042,"uid":124942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:55:04.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"10ce57369375be0c482ec6a331eda9cf514db740","tid":414042,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:55:50.000Z","msg":"有，親人離開，精神病，etc...."},{"pid":"c06546cac2207cde21076ed2b18aea7bf7a1dcee","tid":414042,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:56:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">無事唔洗擔心</span><br />\n相愛過後平淡係好正常"},{"pid":"653753a035669a9637a7b34238f97fb2873d4be2","tid":414042,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"認真答，你點發你老婆脾氣先？？？<br />\n呢點好重要"},{"pid":"4599a5b5b0413af01ceaabdc25033b91264b14a1","tid":414042,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有，親人離開，精神病，etc....</blockquote><br />\n大把啦<br />\n仲有負資產 俾人炒"},{"pid":"a684cd546d3f8ba3511d1fd3a18d050942a55b2f","tid":414042,"uid":124942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答，你點發你老婆脾氣先？？？<br />\n呢點好重要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係發自己脾氣，話自己冇用，話自己冇晒信心，再令唔倒佢開心，叫佢想離婚就同我離，大家喊晒咁<br />\n<br />\n我都知自己衰衝動講咗句最唔應該講嘅說話，但係果一吓真係控制唔倒自己！唉，而家都唔知點先可以氹返自己老婆，道歉過後已經盡量扮冇事，但係佢依然對我好冷淡，佢一對我冷淡我又好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ee1508c8c45ea2e448a73eb8b5beeaa818a213","tid":414042,"uid":124942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">無事唔洗擔心</span><br />\n相愛過後平淡係好正常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家係冷淡，並唔係平淡，大家喺間屋度冇咩嘢傾，嚴格嚟講係佢唔係咁想應我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}